This paper deals with optimal control of dynamical systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of sampling-based algorithms, which are commonly used in robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of path integral methods, which are often used in machine learning and statistical physics (cs.LG, cs.NE).
